	(MainGUI::checkCurrentFaceIndex):
	s/numberOfFaces/currentNumberOfFaces/.
	(MainGUI::checkCurrentInstanceIndex): Renamed to...
	(MainGUI::checkCurrentNamedInstanceIndex): ...this.
