	* src/ftcommon.c (strcasecmp): Define to `_stricmp' if not
	available.

	* src/ftview.c (snprintf): Define to `_snprintf' if not available.

2006-05-12  Werner Lemberg  <wl@gnu.org>


	* Version 2.2.1 released.
	=========================


